            <history-note id="DLM2160026"><amended-provision>Section 27(2)(e)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 May 2002</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM48916">section 11</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Credit (Repossession) Amendment Act 1999</amending-leg> (1999 No 127).</history-note>
